      "title": "Cycle lane from Port City to Armour Street",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Colombo Municipal Council introduced a new lane for cyclists in Colombo City.",
        "The CMC introduced the new cycling land and cycle parking facility in Colombo.",
        "The CMC adopted this measure as a solution to the fuel crisis.",
        "The first cycle land is from the Colombo Port City to Armour Street, and it was declared open by Rosy Senanayake, the Mayoress of Colombo."
      ],
